# Defense-in-depth: even if someone runs `git add media/` manually,
# only files matching the slideshow's allowlist should reach the index.
# This list MUST stay in sync with:
#   - scripts/generate-media-json.js  (VALID_EXTENSIONS)
#   - sync-media.ps1                  ($ValidExtensions)
#   - app.js                          (IMAGE_EXTENSIONS, VIDEO_EXTENSIONS)
#
# Strategy: ignore everything, then un-ignore valid media extensions.

*

# Allow this gitignore itself
!.gitignore

# Image formats the player understands
!*.jpg
!*.jpeg
!*.JPG
!*.JPEG
!*.png
!*.PNG
!*.webp
!*.WEBP
!*.gif
!*.GIF
!*.bmp
!*.BMP
!*.avif
!*.AVIF

# Video formats the player understands
!*.mp4
!*.MP4
!*.webm
!*.WEBM
